{"tid":449976,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★工作問題不開心 60後墮樓亡！","createTime":"2017-10-27T16:40:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-28T04:02:07.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"63d4421550e4cc1ed75a146a2d23326bd4b64b1f","tid":449976,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T16:40:48.000Z","msg":"發佈日期：2017-10-27 22:14<br />\n<br />\n今日（27日）下午2時許，警方接獲報案指，發現一名男子倒臥東區醫院內一附屬宿舍對開山坡，救護員到場證實事主明顯死亡，毋需送院。警員到場調查，初步證實男事主為一名49歲姓鄭的東區醫院職員，估計他由一建築物天台墮下，東區醫院行政總監劉楚釗醫生及三名職員到現場。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，死者為東區醫院義肢及矯形部主管鄭子傑，他亦是香港截肢者協會團隊的義肢矯形師，專門為截肢後病人提供長遠跟進及調整服務，過去曾接受傳媒訪問，疑<span style=\"color: red;\">因工作問題不開心</span>。<br />\n<br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/937768/xlarge/405e820b5600bbb326294e8f1b116bc8.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F937768%2Fxlarge%2F405e820b5600bbb326294e8f1b116bc8.jpg&d=gY1fSsj08t5UlW5IFkmIwlKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=381b7ebc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/937768/xlarge/405e820b5600bbb326294e8f1b116bc8.jpg</a><br />\n[/img]<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/港聞/128955/東區醫院49歲義肢矯形部主管墮樓亡-疑因工作問題尋死\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2F128955%2F%E6%9D%B1%E5%8D%80%E9%86%AB%E9%99%A249%E6%AD%B2%E7%BE%A9%E8%82%A2%E7%9F%AF%E5%BD%A2%E9%83%A8%E4%B8%BB%E7%AE%A1%E5%A2%AE%E6%A8%93%E4%BA%A1-%E7%96%91%E5%9B%A0%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C%E5%B0%8B%E6%AD%BB&d=gY1fSsj08t5UlW5IFkmIwlKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=eac5d34b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/港聞/128955/東區醫院49歲義肢矯形部主管墮樓亡-疑因工作問題尋死</a>"},{"pid":"deb8b5fdb4a715ddb804aca397236cdece631547","tid":449976,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T16:41:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 